sentences: Zulema de la Cruz Castillejo (born 9 March 1958) is a Spanish pianist and composer.
After completing her studies, she took a position as professor in Electroacoustic Composition at the Madrid Conservatory in 1988.
De la Cruz has performed with Sax Ensemble since 1993, and also with Fundación Sax.
